    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
      <span class="bg-[#110833] border border-[rgba(124,58,237,0.3)] text-[#7C3AED] text-[11px] font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Guide pratique · Microsoft 365</span>
